data.title: Dog lovers!
data.message: {"time":1607511156040,"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"The loyalty and devotion that dogs demonstrate as part of their natural instincts as pack animals closely mimics the human idea of love and friendship, leading many dog owners to view their pets as full-fledged family members."}}],"version":"2.19.0"}
